{"type": "article", "id": 10063, "title": "大理石切割花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-27T07:37:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140235SUaRD8mpNK9icG1u.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t大理石的身上究竟有多少种被雕琢的可能？设计师 Paolo Ulian 和 Moreno Ratti 协作推出了一套大理石切割花瓶系列，这些花瓶被一层一层内进，切成 4 毫米厚的同心薄环，有的是圆形切割，有的则呈现五边形，三角形和花瓣形状，柔软的切割形状和大理石的坚硬融合在一起，简约而又别致。这是 <a href=\"http://www.morenoratti.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Moreno Ratti 的个人主页</a>，以及<a href=\"http://www.paoloulian.it/\" target=\"_blank\"> Paolo Ulian 的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140232HQrxm5Xe06BchdTV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140232DwW2ZzymGtbR1h6M.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061402333ztnsI6PAuJHLF4c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061402335gLPm9QtoXiDWCOV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140233X20dRDm89vkrhifU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140234GEI6pfVnvAUiw5kR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140234GCdUyPxQqFiswgS2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}